---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
import Content from '~/components/widgets/Content.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Custom Tooling & Automation — rebel-state',
  description: 'Build bespoke middleware, dashboards, and automation to eliminate manual bottlenecks and scale operations.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <Hero
    tagline="Services"
    title="Custom Tooling & Automation"
    subtitle="Eliminate manual bottlenecks with bespoke tooling and scalable automation built for your workflows."
    actions={[{ text: 'Contact us', href: '/contact', variant: 'primary' }]}
    image={{ src: '~/assets/images/screen-glasses.jpg', alt: 'Engineers building tooling' }}
  />
  <Content
    items={[
      {
        description: `In the modern enterprise landscape, "off-the-shelf" is often synonymous with "bottleneck." While SaaS platforms offer quick starts, they frequently force businesses to warp their unique workflows to fit the rigid architecture of the software. At rebel-state, we believe the software should serve the business, not the other way around. Our Custom Tooling & Automation service is built on the philosophy of Operational Sovereignty—the idea that a company’s most valuable competitive advantages are found in its specific, proprietary processes.`,
      },
      {
        description: `<img src="/assets/images/do-something-great.jpg" alt="Automation workflow" class="w-full rounded-lg mb-4"/>\n\nThe hidden cost of manual labor is not just the hourly wage; it is the cognitive load and the inevitable human error that slows down scaling. We begin our process with a deep-tissue audit of your current stack. We look for the "glue work"—those tedious tasks where employees are moving data from one window to another, or manually reconciling reports. By building bespoke digital infrastructure, we eliminate these friction points. Whether it’s a custom middleware that connects legacy ERP systems to modern cloud environments or a specialized internal dashboard that streamlines project management, our tools are designed for high performance and zero bloat.`,
      },
      {
        description: `Automation at rebel-state goes beyond simple "If This Then That" logic. We architect robust, scalable systems using modern languages and frameworks that ensure longevity. We prioritize modularity; as your business grows, your tools evolve with you. We handle everything from API development and integration to the creation of standalone desktop or web applications that solve specific industry challenges. By automating the mundane, we allow your human capital to focus on what humans do best: strategy, creativity, and high-level problem-solving. In a world where speed is the primary currency, our custom tools act as a force multiplier for your entire organization.`,
      },
    ]}
  />
</Layout>
